Phelps Dodge Corp said it filed aregistration statement with the Securities and ExchangeCommission for an offering of four mln depositary shares.    Each depositary share represents one quarter share of aconvertible exchange preference share. The liquidationpreference of each depositary share is 50 dlrs.    Quarterly dividends on the preference shares are cumulativeand are payable beginning July 1, 1987.    Proceeds will be used to redeem outstanding five dlrconvertible exchangeable preference shares, to repay bank debtand for general corporate purposes. Reuter&#3;